		<h2>Help</h2>
		<div class="col">
			<h3>Getting Started</h3>
			<p>Welcome to the Aberrant Character Sheet. This help section will guide you through using the sheet.</p>
			<h4>Tabs</h4>
			<ul>
				<li><strong>Abilities:</strong> Manage your character's attributes, abilities, and enhancements</li>
				<li><strong>Quantum:</strong> Track quantum powers, quantum and taint</li>
				<li><strong>Combat:</strong> Handle initiative, movement, weapons, health, and soak values</li>
				<li><strong>Info:</strong> Character background and information</li>
				<li><strong>Config:</strong> Configure sheet settings and preferences</li>
			</ul>
        </div>
		<div class="col">
			<h3>Rolling Dice</h3>
			<p>Click on the d10 icon next to an ability, power, or attack to roll dice. The system uses d10 dice pools with successes counted on 7+.
                10s explode and 1s cancel successes.</p>
			
			<h4>Mega Attributes</h4>
			<p>Mega attributes allow you to roll a larger pool of dice for key attributes.
                To use a mega attribute, simply click on the button next to the desired attribute.
                This will roll a pool of dice equal to the mega attribute value plus any relevant bonuses.
                The mega attribute roll button will appear automatically on some ability rolls. Click on it to use it.</p>
		</div>
        <div class="col">
            <h3>Sheet Configuration</h3>
            <h4>Edit Mode</h4>
            <p>The config tab allows you to toggle edit mode on and off. When edit mode is enabled, you can modify character details directly on the sheet.</p>
            <h4>Mega Attributes over 5</h4>
            <p>By default, mega attributes are capped at 5. You can enable the option to allow mega attributes to exceed 5 in the config tab.</p>
            <h4>Display Chrysalis</h4>
            <p>Enable this option in the config tab to show Chrysalis-related fields on the sheet.</p>
        </div>
